metadata.name: Where Are The Pepes In My Mind Map? #1
metadata.description:
‘WHERE IS PEPE’ GAME RULES
-Find all the Pepe the Frog characters (~20)
-Share your findings to my Discord
-1st 30 people to find them all get a free Pepe NFT, and will be the first members of my community

BUYING THIS NFT
If the highest bid is:
1 ETH - bidder gets a Pepe gallery in our upcoming metaverse platform
3 ETH - bidder gets Pepe gallery + coworking space in platform
10 ETH - bidder gets Pepe museum + Pepe item in platform

60% of bid I will use to buy my members’ NFT art
40% will be for leading my artist life, and for our metaverse project

I’m a small artist, so am looking for project partners who can help design our NFTs and our world. Our platform is in progress - stay tuned by following my Twitter and Discord for more details.
